name: I don't know
description:
Piece #4 of the collection:
I'm not your therapist but I'd like to cheer you up with my dorky art.

The series focuses on the fragility of the inner world and brings up topics that we often find in our long journey on earth. 

I don't know. I don't know what I want. 
I don't know where I want to go. 
I don't know what is good for me.
I don't know.

Sometimes in life, it is good to accept that I don't know.
